== v0.2.3 (2014-09-07)

* Use datepicker out of jquery-ui.
* Included custom jquery-ui theme, that is css & images.
* Clicking outside of the widget to close popup windows.

== v0.2.2 (2014-06-15)

* Memorial events will be marked with starts.
* Tidied up resizing code.

== v0.2.1 (2014-02-06)

 * Fix the height of the details window in relation to
   very long descriptions.

== v0.2.0 (2014-02-06)

 * Works with older versions of jQuery.
 * Resize to fit just within the enclosing element.
 * Scroll aware positioning of the popup windows.
 * Display 'location' in the details.
 * Now it's proof against the Closure Compiler.
 * Small fix in CSS.

== v0.1.0 (2014-02-03)

 * Initial version.
